sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CLI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as KubeRay Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant Controller as RayCluster Controller
    participant K8sResources as Kubernetes Resources
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>6379/TCP GCS<br/>8265/TCP Dashboard
    participant RayWorker as Ray Worker Pods
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,RayWorker: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply RayCluster<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (user creds)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-ray-io-v1-raycluster<br/>Auth: mTLS (API server cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Response
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-ray-io-v1-raycluster<br/>Auth: mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutation Response
    K8sAPI-->>User: RayCluster Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch RayCluster CRDs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: RayCluster Event

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Ray Head Pod<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Ray Worker Pods<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pods Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Services, ConfigMaps<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Resources Created

    Controller->>RayHead: Health Check<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    RayHead-->>Controller: 200 OK

    RayWorker->>RayHead: Connect to GCS<br/>6379/TCP (Optional mTLS)
    RayHead-->>RayWorker: Connection Established

    Note over User,RayWorker: Flow 2: RayJob Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply RayJob<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: RayJob Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch RayJob CRDs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: RayJob Event

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Cluster Created

    Controller->>RayHead: Submit Job<br/>10001/TCP (Optional mTLS)
    RayHead->>RayWorker: Distribute Tasks<br/>Dynamic Ports (Optional mTLS)
    RayWorker-->>RayHead: Task Results
    RayHead-->>Controller: Job Complete

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update RayJob Status<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Status Updated

    Note over User,RayWorker: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (no auth)
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus Metrics
